text: læa meux di thuk klaw kæ phwk khea wa cng ptibati tam sing thi xallxh di thrng prathan lng ma theid phwk khea k klaw wa midi rea catæibati sing thi rea di phb brrda brrphburusʹ khxng rea khey ptibati ma theanan læa mæ di prakt wa brrphburusʹ khxng phwk khea mi kheacı sing dı læa thang mi di rab næwthang xan thuk txng ktam kranan hrux
